Pick n Pay of South Africa Says it Plans to Fire About 8% of Its Workforce

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-07-06T10:20:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/pick-n-pay-of-south-africa-says-it-plans-to-fire-about-8-of-its-workforce.html
Pick n Pay Stores Ltd. (PIK)  said it plans
to fire about 8 percent of its workforce.  The Cape Town-based company said in an e-mail today that it
aims to cut 3,137 jobs.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  